VMINVR Changelog

1.3:
+ Add support for 2.6.XX kernel.  Still supports 2.4.XX kernel. -RMC

1.2:
+ Add fixupflags for RedHat9. -DLH

1.1:

1.0.2:
+ Add support for PC4-7301 and IOMAX-8451. -DLH

1.0.1:
+ Add Makefile to tests directory. -DLH
+ Fix compiler warnings in test code. -DLH
+ Split up complex functions. - DLH
+ Switch to Linus's code style. -DLH
+ Documentation edits. -DLH
+ Use Xinclude to get latest example code. -DLH
+ Add support for CPCI-7350. -DLH

1.0:
+ Skip mmap() test in interface_test.c mmap() for non-page-aligned NVRAM.
  Treat mmap() as unsupported on these boards because the behavior is
  inconsistant between different versions of glibc. -DLH
+ Fix the path the kernel source to use Linus's decreed standard. -DLH

0.3:
+ Fix address and size on VMICPCI-7699. -DLH

0.2:
+ Use miscdevice interface. -DLH
+ Add phys_addr and size module parameters. -DLH
+ Documentation edits. -DLH
+ Fix buggy address test in mmap(). -DLH
+ Fix incorrect device id for FPGA device. -DLH

0.1:
+ Initial testing release of the NVRAM. -DLH

